## Push

示例

```ts
type Result = Push<[1, 2], "3">; // [1, 2, '3']
```

实现

```ts
// Push
type Push<T extends unknown[], U> = [...T, U];
// unShift 的实现
type Unshift<T extends unknown[], U> = [U, ...T];
```
